org.apache.poi.hssf.model

Class InternalWorkbook

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.model.InternalWorkbook

  • @Internal
public final class InternalWorkbook
extends java.lang.Object
    Low level model implementation of a Workbook. Provides creational methods for settings and objects contained in the workbook object.

    This file contains the low level binary records starting at the workbook's BOF and ending with the workbook's EOF. Use HSSFWorkbook for a high level representation.

    The structures of the highlevel API use references to this to perform most of their operations. Its probably unwise to use these low level structures directly unless you really know what you're doing. I recommend you read the Microsoft Excel 97 Developer's Kit (Microsoft Press) and the documentation at http://sc.openoffice.org/excelfileformat.pdf before even attempting to use this.

    (工作簿的低级模型实现。为工作簿对象中包含的设置和对象提供创建方法。此文件包含从工作簿的BOF开始并以工作簿的收件箱结束的低级二进制记录。使用HSSFWorkbook进行高级表示。高级API的结构使用对此的引用来执行大部分操作。除非您真正知道自己在做什么，否则直接使用这些低级结构可能是不明智的。我建议您在尝试使用它之前先阅读Microsoft Excel 97开发人员套件（Microsoft Press）和http://sc.openoffice.org/excelfileformat.pdf上的文档。)
    See Also:
    HSSFWorkbook

        public static final java.lang.String[] WORKBOOK_DIR_ENTRY_NAMES
        Normally, the Workbook will be in a POIFS Stream called "Workbook". However, some weird XLS generators use "WORKBOOK" or "BOOK".(通常，工作簿将位于名为“工作簿”的POIFS流中。然而，一些奇怪的XLS生成器使用“WORKBOOK”或“BOOK”。)

    • Method Detail

      • createWorkbook

        public static InternalWorkbook createWorkbook(java.util.List<Record> recs)
        read support for low level API. Pass in an array of Record objects, A Workbook object is constructed and passed back with all of its initialization set to the passed in records and references to those records held. Unlike Sheet workbook does not use an offset (its assumed to be 0) since its first in a file. If you need an offset then construct a new array with a 0 offset or write your own ;-p.(支持低级别API。传递一个Record对象数组，构建并传递回Workbook对象，其所有初始化都设置为传递的记录和对所保存的记录的引用。与工作表不同，工作簿自文件中的第一个以来就不使用偏差（假设为0）。如果您需要一个偏置量，请构造一个具有0偏置量的新数组或编写您自己的;-p.)
        Parameters:
        recs - an array of Record objects(recs -Record对象数组)
        Returns:
        Workbook object(Workbook对象)

      • changeExternalReference

        public boolean changeExternalReference(java.lang.String oldUrl,
                                       java.lang.String newUrl)
        Changes an external referenced file to another file. A formular in Excel which refers a cell in another file is saved in two parts: The referenced file is stored in an reference table. the row/cell information is saved separate. This method invokation will only change the reference in the lookup-table itself.(将外部参照文件更改为另一个文件。Excel中引用另一个文件中单元格的公式分为两部分：引用的文件存储在引用表中。行/单元格信息单独保存。此方法调用仅会更改查找表本身中的引用。)
        Parameters:
        oldUrl - The old URL to search for and which is to be replaced(oldUrl -要搜索且将被替换的旧URL)
        newUrl - The URL replacement(newUrl -URL替换)
        Returns:
        true if the oldUrl was found and replaced with newUrl. Otherwise false(如果找到旧Url并替换为newUrl，则为真。否则为false)
